               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420228-name-1300" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1300" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1300" type="surname" value="COSSEIN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1300" type="given" value="HAJI"></interp>HAJI COSSEIN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">through an interpreter.</hi>) I had a watch and guard, and key, on board my vessel—it was safe in my box at four o'clock, I do not know what day—about five my box was broken open, and they were gone—this is the watch—(<hi rend="italic">looking at one</hi>)—the prisoner was on board that day—I asked him if he took my watch—he wanted to strike me, and I let him go.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. CLARKSON</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How many Lascars were there on board? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Three or four—I am serjeant on board the vessel, the prisoner was a sepoy—I was on board before him—he shipped at Bombay.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420228-name-1301" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1301" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1301" type="surname" value="STEVENS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1301" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES STEVENS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker—this watch was pledged by Mary McCarthy on the 22nd of February, for 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., in the name of Mary McCarthy—she said it was for a Lascar.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420228-name-1302" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1302" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1302" type="surname" value="MCCARTHY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420228-name-1302" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY MCCARTHY</persName>
                  </hi>. I cohabit with the prisoner—he gave me this watch to pledge-there was a chain besides, but a navigator broke that from my neck.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You are an unfortunate woman? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I have seen seven or eight Lascars from the ship at different times—none of them besides the prisoner have slept with me—he slept with me last Tues<lb></lb>day week, and gave me four or five shillings-we have never quarrelled I swear—he can speak a little broken English.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
